《平价正义》
ONE DOLLAR LAWYER

5
00:00:10,250 --> 00:00:11,420
《第2集》
EPISODE 2

6
00:00:20,430 --> 00:00:22,260
这就是你的证据吗
This is your evidence?

7
00:00:22,350 --> 00:00:25,730
对 你没有理由反对提交
Yes. Do you object to the submission

