同意
Yes.

11
00:00:44,330 --> 00:00:46,710
审判长和各位陪审员
Your Honor, and ladies and gentlemen of the jury,

12
00:00:46,790 --> 00:00:48,250
请仔细看
look very carefully.

13
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:52,840
可以证明被告无罪的证据 就在这个箱子里
The evidence to prove the defendant's innocence is in this box.

14
00:01:04,600 --> 00:01:05,720
里面有东西吗
Is there anything in it?

15
00:01:06,730 --> 00:01:09,020
-没有 -你看见了什么
-No. -What do you see?

16
00:01:09,100 --> 00:01:10,650
什么都看不见
I don't see anything.

17
