根本没有能够证明被告无罪的证据
there isn't a single evidence to prove the defendant's innocence.

19
00:01:19,740 --> 00:01:21,530
因为没有证据可以证明被告无罪
There's no evidence proving his innocence,

20
00:01:21,620 --> 00:01:24,120
所以大家就认为被告有罪 对吧
so, we can think that the defendant is guilty, can't we?

21
00:01:24,700 --> 00:01:28,750
那么大家这就是在推定被告有罪
Then, you are all making the assumption that the defendant is guilty.

22
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:32,750
但在韩国的法律中 虽然存在无罪推定原则
However, in Korean Law, one is innocent until proven guilty,

23
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,630
但却没有有罪推定原则
but one isn't guilty until proven innocent.

24
00:01:34,710 --> 00:01:36,420
这也就是说
What I'm saying is,

25
00:01:36,710 --> 00:01:40,970
任何人不能因为被告有四次前科记录
just because the defendant has four previous convictions,

26
00:01:41,050 --> 00:01:45,260
就推定他有罪
none of us should presume that he is guilty.

27
00:01:45,350 --> 00:01:46,890
《刑事诉讼法》第307条
Article 307 of the Criminal Procedure Act,

28
00:01:47,100 --> 00:01:49,100
要依据证据来认定事实
"Fact-finding must be based on evidence."

29
00:01:49,230 --> 00:01:50,730
这就是证据裁判主义
It's the principle of trial by evidence.

30
00:01:50,810 --> 00:01:52,810
我们不能推定某人有罪
We don't presume one's guilt,

31
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:55,860
必须要依据确凿的证据来进行举证
but it must be proven through definitive evidence

32
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:57,900
而证明被告有罪的责任
and it is up to the prosecutor…

33
00:02:00,030 --> 00:02:00,990
在于检察官
to prove his guilt.

34
00:02:01,070 --> 00:02:02,820
那么白玛丽检察官
All right, Prosecutor Baek.

35
00:02:03,410 --> 00:02:06,950
请在这个箱子里放入可以证明
Please put in the evidence that the defendant is guilty

36
00:02:07,870 --> 00:02:08,910
被告有罪的证据
into this box.

37
00:02:19,340 --> 00:02:20,420
这里没有…
There is…

38
00:02:22,050 --> 00:02:23,090
证据
no evidence.

39
00:02:26,930 --> 00:02:29,520
被告试图偷取证人的钱包
There's only the witness's testimony that the defendant tried to steal his wallet.

40
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:30,810
这只是证人的一面之词
There's only the witness's testimony that the defendant tried to steal his wallet.

41
00:02:31,390 --> 00:02:32,190
我方有异议
Objection.

42
00:02:33,270 --> 00:02:35,190
若本案件是盗窃案件的话
If this was a case about theft,

43
00:02:35,270 --> 00:02:36,900
就会有明确的证物
we'd have clear evidence,

44
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:38,610
但因为本案件是盗窃未遂
but it was only attempted,

45
00:02:38,690 --> 00:02:41,070
所以只能通过间接的证据进行判断
so, we can only judge by circumstantial evidence.

46
00:02:41,650 --> 00:02:42,910
对 检方的观点很对
Yes, that's a great point.

47
00:02:42,990 --> 00:02:47,080
正因如此 检察官更应该要证明
That's all the more reason for you to prove

48
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:49,910
被告是否真的有
whether the defendant had any motive

49
00:02:50,790 --> 00:02:52,080
盗取钱包的意图
to steal.

50
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:54,210
也只有这样才能够证明检方在公诉中
That way, as the prosecution claimed,

51
00:02:54,290 --> 00:02:58,340
提到的盗窃未遂嫌疑是事实
the theft attempt charge would be proven to be true.

52
00:02:58,420 --> 00:02:59,840
被告在检察机关的 调查过程中已经自首
The defendant has already

53
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:01,220
被告在检察机关的 调查过程中已经自首
admitted his guilt and confessed while being examined by the prosecution.

54
00:03:01,300 --> 00:03:02,840
并且提交了检讨书
admitted his guilt and confessed while being examined by the prosecution.

55
00:03:02,930 --> 00:03:04,050
被告为何会这么做呢
Why would he have done that?

56
