00:32:45,540 --> 00:32:46,500
真尴尬
How embarrassing.

511
00:32:47,210 --> 00:32:50,090
-好笑吧 -不好笑 别闹了
-Isn't it funny? -It isn't funny. Stop.

512
00:32:50,170 --> 00:32:52,590
反正你一个人也忙不过来
You can't do this on your own anyway, Mr. Cheon.

513
00:32:53,210 --> 00:32:55,090
一起工作的话肯定会更好
It'll be nice to work together.

514
00:32:55,170 --> 00:32:58,220
如果在凌晨接到案子也可以一起分担
If you get a case early in the morning, it'll be better to accept it together.

515
00:32:58,640 --> 00:33:00,640
好像没什么不好
What is there not to like about this?

516
00:33:00,720 --> 00:33:01,810
你们俩是一伙的吧
You two have teamed up.

517
00:33:01,890 --> 00:33:04,850
事务长 有什么好的
Mr. Sa. What is good about working together?

518
00:33:04,930 --> 00:33:06,640
她工作干得好才能对我们有帮助
It's only good if she's good at her job.

519
00:33:06,730 --> 00:33:08,440
但上次在法庭上你没看见吗 她工作能力很差
Didn't you see her at court? She's horrible.

520
00:33:11,690 --> 00:33:13,530
看来你对我有些误解
There must have been a misunderstanding.

521
00:33:13,820 --> 00:33:15,690
你知道误解是什么意思吗
You know what "misunderstanding" means, don't you?

522
00:33:15,780 --> 00:33:17,490
知道 你不是真的要在这里实习 对吧
I know. You don't mean it, do you?

523
00:33:17,570 --> 00:33:19,990
我疯了吗 在这种地方实习？
Are you crazy? Why would I want to work here?

524
00:33:20,120 --> 00:33:21,530
而且还是在你手下？
And under you at that?

525
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,620
你看看
You see that?

526
00:33:24,160 --> 00:33:26,750
我说让她在这里实习 但她自己不愿意啊
I said I'd give her the job, but she says she doesn't want it.

527
00:33:26,830 --> 00:33:28,710
那我能怎么办啊
What can I do? Hmm.

528
00:33:29,540 --> 00:33:31,170
出口在那边
The door is over there.

529
00:33:33,880 --> 00:33:37,130
你们打扫一下吧 办公室这样子 谁会来啊
Why don't you clean up? Who would come to an office like this?

530
00:33:37,220 --> 00:33:40,680
你应该把拖欠的月租交上 把办公室也打扫一下
You should pay your overdue rent and clean up this mess, okay?

531
00:33:41,300 --> 00:33:42,470
好的
Okay.

532
00:33:43,810 --> 00:33:45,310
你可以把想说的话都说完再走
Say all you want to say before you go.

533
00:33:49,690 --> 00:33:50,900
那个…
But…

534
00:33:53,770 --> 00:33:56,610
真是的 好吃吗
Come on. Is it good?

535
00:33:56,690 --> 00:33:58,150
就那样吧
I'm just eating it.

536
00:34:03,240 --> 00:34:04,830
他为什么在这里啊
Geez. Why is that guy here?

537
00:34:05,370 --> 00:34:07,200
真是的 爷爷也太过分了
Darn it! This is going too far, Grandpa.

538
00:34:18,010 --> 00:34:18,880
爷爷
Grandpa!

539
00:34:19,380 --> 00:34:21,180
你为什么要这样对我
How could you do that to me?

540
00:34:21,260 --> 00:34:22,840
你怎么现在就回来了
Back already?

541
00:34:22,930 --> 00:34:24,640
怎么了 千律师不让你在那里实习吗
Why? He wouldn't let you work there?

542
00:34:24,720 --> 00:34:26,600
-什么 -真是的
-What? -Gosh.

543
00:34:27,220 --> 00:34:31,520
我没跟那边提前打招呼 就让你过去 虽然有些担心
I was worried as I sent you there without any notice.

544
00:34:31,850 --> 00:34:34,060
但我还以为你自己能够解决这点小事
I thought you'd be able to handle that on your own.

545
00:34:34,730 --> 00:34:35,860
爷爷 不是这样的…
Grandpa, you see--

546
00:34:35,940 --> 00:34:38,990
也是 他在庭审的时候 就已经知道你的实力了
I know. He saw how you were during the trial, so--

547
00:34:39,070 --> 00:34:41,990
不是 是我自己不愿意在那里实习
No. I don't want to work there. Me.

548
00:34:42,950 --> 00:34:43,910
为什么不愿意
Why not?

549
00:34:43,990 --> 00:34:46,910
我不想在一个为了几分钱 就帮别人善后的律师手下学习
I don't want to work for someone who picks up after others for chump change.

550
00:34:46,990 --> 00:34:49,040
那你还不是输给了那样的律师
Then, what about you who lost to a lawyer like that?

551
00:34:50,250 --> 00:34:51,710
那个时候 我…
That time, I was…

552
00:34:51,790 --> 00:34:55,040
那场庭审就算是我同样也会输
Even I would have lost that trial

553
00:34:56,340 --> 00:34:59,420
输给那个为了一点钱 就帮别人善后的律师
to that lawyer who picks up after others for chump change.

554
00:35:00,170 --> 00:35:01,970
收多少委托费
How much a lawyer makes

555
00:35:02,050 --> 00:35:05,640
并不代表一名律师的能力
doesn't define the skills of that lawyer.

556
00:35:05,720 --> 00:35:08,220
这我也知道 但是千律师有点奇怪
I know that too, but he's kind of weird.

557
00:35:08,310 --> 00:35:09,600
而且他的办公室也很脏
His office is dirty too.

558
00:35:09,680 --> 00:35:12,350
就待两个月 不会再多了
It's only two months, no more than that.

559
00:35:13,060 --> 00:35:14,560
这样你也干不了吗
You still can't do it?

560
00:35:15,940 --> 00:35:18,530
你为什么想让我去那里实习
Why do you want me to work there so much?

561
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:24,700
因为我们白法律事务所
That's because…

562
00:35:26,370 --> 00:35:28,200
没有像他一样的律师
he's the kind of lawyer we don't have at Baek.

563
00:35:37,040 --> 00:35:38,920
一号航站楼

564
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:41,300
天啊 我儿子很辛苦吧
My goodness. My son has been working so hard, hasn't he?

565
00:35:42,510 --> 00:35:43,720
没有
No, I haven't.

566
00:35:44,340 --> 00:35:47,890
怎么没有啊 你看起来那么憔悴
I know you have. Your look so worn out.

567
00:35:48,100 --> 00:35:49,890
我都多大了 你还这样
I'm too old for this.

568
00:35:49,970 --> 00:35:52,770
你结婚生子以后 就知道孩子有多可爱了
Get married and have a child. You'll know how cute they are.

569
00:35:52,850 --> 00:35:54,230
对吧 我也该结婚了
I should get married, right?

570
00:35:54,310 --> 00:35:55,850
