Yes. It's time for me to do it.

576
00:36:09,910 --> 00:36:11,290
她应该会喜欢的吧
This would be good enough, won't it?

577
00:36:11,370 --> 00:36:14,080
-多少钱 -这个？五万美金
-How much was it? -This? 50,000 dollars.

578
00:36:14,160 --> 00:36:17,080
你小子真是的 我不是让你省着点花吗
Come on, son. I told you to be frugal.

579
00:36:17,170 --> 00:36:19,170
这都是投资
It's all an investment.

580
00:36:19,290 --> 00:36:20,750
这算什么投资啊
That isn't investment.

581
00:36:21,250 --> 00:36:24,010
但是一枚戒指值一辆车的钱吗
Anyway, a ring costs as much as a car?

582
00:36:24,090 --> 00:36:27,140
但是这应该比你 赔在股市里的钱要少点吧
I think it would be less than what you lost trading stocks.

583
00:36:28,600 --> 00:36:30,180
你已经知道了？你妈妈也知道吗
Did you know about that? Mom too?

584
00:36:30,310 --> 00:36:32,270
如果妈妈知道 你就不会在这里了
If Mom knew, you wouldn't be here.

585
00:36:32,350 --> 00:36:35,190
但五万美金也有点多啊
Even so, 50,000 dollars is too much.

586
00:36:35,560 --> 00:36:38,980
爸 想要得到像玛丽一样的女人
Dad, if you want to get a woman like Mari,

587
00:36:39,060 --> 00:36:41,020
这些钱一定要花
you have to spend this much.

588
00:36:42,150 --> 00:36:43,690
你不是说过
Didn't you say you wanted

589
00:36:43,990 --> 00:36:47,950
想要把白法律事务所 变成白与徐法律事务所吗
to change Baek Law Firm into Baek & Seo Law Firm?

590
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:54,040
徐民赫 看来你已经长大了
You're all grown up, Minhyeok.

591
00:36:54,660 --> 00:36:56,960
我感觉我还在长 走吧
I think I'm still growing. Let's go.

592
00:36:58,580 --> 00:37:00,380
-你有信心吗 -当然
-Do you think you can do it? -Of course.

593
00:37:01,130 --> 00:37:03,000
-马上就要成了 -很好
-I'm almost there. -Good.

594
