00:37:21,980 --> 00:37:23,020
千律师
Hey, Mr. Cheon.

598
00:37:46,670 --> 00:37:48,680
律师事务所 二楼
LAWYER'S OFFICE, 2F

599
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:51,180
他到底去哪里了
Where the heck did he go? Hmm.

