00:38:03,770 --> 00:38:04,940
谢谢
Thank you.

601
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,530
你们接着聊
Continue your conversation.

602
00:38:13,070 --> 00:38:16,040
汝真咖啡馆 律师事务所 二楼

603
00:38:29,840 --> 00:38:31,680
谢武长 事务长
OFFICE MANAGER, SA MUJANG

604
00:38:33,350 --> 00:38:34,600
千智勋 代表律师
CHIEF COUNSEL, CHEON JIHUN

605
00:38:39,060 --> 00:38:40,190
喂
Hey.

606
00:38:41,140 --> 00:38:42,560
你这是在干什么
What are you doing right now?

607
00:38:44,310 --> 00:38:45,860
你来了 千智勋律师
You're here, Mr. Cheon Jihun.

608
00:38:52,320 --> 00:38:53,700
我在打扫卫生
I was just cleaning.

609
00:38:53,780 --> 00:38:55,030
你为什么要打扫卫生
Why were you cleaning?

610
00:38:55,120 --> 00:38:56,740
我没法在脏乱的环境里做事
I can't work in a dirty environment.

611
00:38:56,830 --> 00:38:58,580
谁要在脏乱的环境里做事啊
Who's going to work in a dirty environment?

612
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:02,210
我打算在这里实习
I'd like to work as a probationary employee here.

613
00:39:09,710 --> 00:39:11,170
今天导航没有带错路吗
Did the GPS direct you correctly today?

614
00:39:11,800 --> 00:39:14,800
你又来了这里
You came by the same office again, you know.

615
00:39:15,970 --> 00:39:18,180
你不是说你没法在这样的 事务所里做事吗
Didn't you say you couldn't work in an office like this?

616
00:39:18,680 --> 00:39:20,520
不久前
You were the one...

617
00:39:22,020 --> 00:39:23,270
你还瞧不起我神圣的办公室
...who insulted my sacred office.

618
00:39:23,350 --> 00:39:26,610
现在又忽然过来 这应该怎么说
Coming here all of a sudden and being like this is so…

619
00:39:28,190 --> 00:39:29,280
太厚脸皮了
awfully shameless.

620
00:39:31,740 --> 00:39:33,780
对于昨天我所做的一切 我很抱歉
Yes. I'm sorry about yesterday.

621
00:39:34,570 --> 00:39:38,370
但是与歉意无关 我确实有点厚脸皮
However, regardless of how sorry I am, I am actually shameless.

622
00:39:38,450 --> 00:39:39,290
有什么问题吗
Is there a problem?

623
00:39:39,370 --> 00:39:41,960
你如此磊落 这让我十分满意
This confidence. I like it very much.

624
00:39:42,040 --> 00:39:45,750
那能麻烦你帮我冲一杯咖啡吗
Then, may I ask you for a cup of coffee, Mari?

625
00:39:46,580 --> 00:39:47,790
深度烘焙咖啡

626
00:39:57,720 --> 00:39:58,720
谢谢 坐下吧
Thanks. Have a seat.

627
00:40:03,690 --> 00:40:04,690
香气很不错
Hmm, nice aroma.

628
00:40:07,110 --> 00:40:08,150
好烫
Ow, hot.

629
00:40:08,980 --> 00:40:11,480
玛丽 我有些事很好奇 所以想问你一下
Mari, I'm curious of something. Let me ask you.

630
00:40:12,110 --> 00:40:15,700
-什么事 -你到底为什么想在这里实习
-Yes? -Why do you really want to work here?

631
00:40:16,990 --> 00:40:18,990
这是因为…
Yes, well… You see.

632
00:40:19,080 --> 00:40:20,450
是因为？
Well?

633
00:40:21,830 --> 00:40:23,580
-其实… -你不会是
-The truth is-- -You haven't been recruited

634
00:40:23,660 --> 00:40:25,870
以在这里实习为条件 被挖到其他律所了吧
elsewhere as long as you worked here temporarily, no?

635
00:40:28,040 --> 00:40:29,420
请你回答
Answer the question.

636
00:40:36,050 --> 00:40:38,850
我在法庭上看到了你全力以赴的样子
After I saw how you did your best during the trial,

637
00:40:38,930 --> 00:40:40,430
就想要在你手下学习
I wanted to learn from you.

638
00:40:40,560 --> 00:40:43,980
所以我不顾羞愧 找到这里来了
That's why I came here to see you even curbing my embarrassment.

639
00:40:46,730 --> 00:40:49,520
但你的表情有些不太好 你现在双唇紧闭啊
But your face speaks otherwise. Your lips are very tight.

640
00:40:52,860 --> 00:40:56,450
好 非常好 我非常满意你这种态度
Good. That's very good. I really like that attitude.

641
00:40:57,530 --> 00:41:01,490
但是我告诉你 一个你不能在这里实习的决定性理由
But let me tell you why you cannot work here as a probationary employee.

642
00:41:01,580 --> 00:41:05,250
你不是说过我是个奇怪的律师吗
Didn't you say that I was a weird lawyer?

643
00:41:05,330 --> 00:41:08,080
是哪个疯子律师申请国民陪审的
What kind of a lunatic lawyer asks for a jury trial?

644
00:41:10,340 --> 00:41:12,460
你不是说我没有作为律师的品格吗
Didn't you say I lack dignity?

645
00:41:12,670 --> 00:41:14,460
最近奇怪的律师怎么这么多
There are so many weird lawyers that lack dignity.

646
00:41:14,550 --> 00:41:16,510
就算行业不景气 律师也要维持品格啊
Isn't there a certain level of professional standard?

647
00:41:17,130 --> 00:41:19,970
在一个既奇怪 又没有品格的律师手下实习
If you work for a lawyer that is weird and undignified,

648
00:41:21,800 --> 00:41:22,850
是不行的
that's no good.

649
00:41:31,230 --> 00:41:32,190
我什么时候说了
When did I say that?

650
00:41:32,270 --> 00:41:35,990
你昨天在法庭上的时候不是说了吗
Didn't you say that at court yesterday?

651
00:41:36,070 --> 00:41:37,610
我什么时候说了啊
When did I say that?

652
00:41:40,320 --> 00:41:41,410
就那个时候啊
That time.

653
00:41:46,830 --> 00:41:47,910
天啊
Oh, my!

654
00:41:48,370 --> 00:41:50,380
玛丽 欢迎你
Welcome, Mari!

655
00:41:51,630 --> 00:41:54,800
欢迎你 热烈欢迎你
My goodness. You are so welcome here.

