-Did you clean the office? -Yes.

658
00:42:02,010 --> 00:42:03,600
天啊 实习第一天就这样
If this is what you did on your first day,

659
00:42:03,810 --> 00:42:05,720
之后会更不一样吧
I can't wait to see how things will change here.

660
00:42:06,770 --> 00:42:08,230
千律师 你还真是有福气啊
You are so lucky, Mr. Cheon.

661
00:42:08,940 --> 00:42:09,980
我可太羡慕了
I'm so jealous.

662
