Mr. Sa. Are you the one who hires the probationary employee?

665
00:42:19,450 --> 00:42:20,910
实习什么实习
No way.

666
00:42:21,660 --> 00:42:22,870
你不能在这里实习
You can't work here.

667
00:42:23,530 --> 00:42:25,870
看在打扫卫生的份上 我也要在这里实习
I'm going to work here. I already cleaned the place up.

668
00:42:26,870 --> 00:42:27,700
不行
No.

669
00:42:27,790 --> 00:42:29,290
我就要在这里实习
I will.

670
00:42:50,020 --> 00:42:51,060
是她吧
Is it her?

671
00:42:52,650 --> 00:42:53,690
是
It's her.

672
00:43:17,340 --> 00:43:19,550
他们是吃错药了吗
Did something happen to these guys?

673
00:43:20,050 --> 00:43:21,550
怎么这么干净
How did it get so clean?

674
00:43:22,180 --> 00:43:24,180
唉唷 他们终于听话了
Gosh. They finally listened to me.

675
00:43:25,510 --> 00:43:28,390
你是昨天那位姑娘啊 千律师去哪里了
You're the lady from yesterday. Did Mr. Cheon go somewhere?

